{"tid":986210,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳門本土派　勢單力弱　澳門獨立運動　初初起步","createTime":"2019-01-18T09:13:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-19T02:22:56.000Z","uid":47714,"like":46,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"5b8b2192e2291b9f5e02337d016d898c45017d8c","tid":986210,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T09:13:50.000Z","msg":"澳門本土派<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nfacebook專頁:<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/abbotmacau\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fabbotmacau&d=lH%2FTjTKhyl%2BMcbfhgwPB7xv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=7d1ac979\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/abbotmacau</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DGGGDZFHpag\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDGGGDZFHpag&d=lH%2FTjTKhyl%2BMcbfhgwPB7xv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=89f715c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DGGGDZFHpag</a><br />\n2017年1月23日<br />\n<br />\n貧僧會戰勝歸來<br />\n<br />\n天有光 如來佛祖夥我靠岸<br />\n刁那星 泊柒錯位抄我八嚿<br />\n流淚了 百萬唐樓供到折墮<br />\n人係廢 派錢放水大眾怯懦<br />\n<br />\n博彩一仆輸爆肛<br />\n隨便搞基建扮傻<br />\n就算商家分贜無禍<br />\n你已在悠長麻木裡<br />\n習慣貪污無力抗<br />\n念眾生 我出山救濠江<br />\n<br />\n吹水安 笨撚廣東話夠正路<br />\n區展新 呃吓公屋選票無壞<br />\n和諧了 你地同鄉會咁愛共<br />\n馮大炮 誓保吸煙萬眾拍和<br />\n<br />\n就算街工不說謊<br />\n全部澳豬愛滅亡<br />\n唔嗌愛國盞打兩鑊<br />\n哪怕係人窮唔柒理<br />\n是非卜亦無謂看<br />\n受到低燈起底幾多個<br />\n<br />\n貧僧會戰勝歸來<br />\n吳區你咪再磋跎<br />\n垃圾貪官罪惡不變改<br />\n有信念難能愚昧再<br />\n開咪勇敢說出來<br />\n講小器 我威絕世代<br />\n<br />\n貧僧會戰勝歸來<br />\n賊首隻腳痛出來<br />\n渡化生蕃澳豬風氣開<br />\n誓殺滅盲從全為愛<br />\n即使戰鬥鍵盤外<br />\n我夢遺與天地同在<br />\n&mdash;------------------------------<br />\n爛過乜鬼的教改<br />\n教畜化身變大王<br />\n十九輕軌千億照袋<br />\n那塊地長年無人理<br />\n免市中心成澤國<br />\n掘晒窿 汽車塞四方<br />\n<br />\n貧僧會戰勝歸來<br />\n學社裡個個『天才』<br />\n面對班官抗爭不變改<br />\n插滿著紅旗人人愛<br />\nAB愛國左膠來<br />\n高生你 比本護照來<br />\n<br />\n貧僧會戰勝歸來<br />\n成班友晚晚開台<br />\n萬眾生蕃伏拜這變改<br />\n六四夜如儀難復再<br />\nBill Vong本土惹青睞<br />\n我夢遺與天地同在<br />\n<br />\n貧僧會戰勝歸來<br />\n貧僧會戰勝歸來<br />\n十八金剛耷到威四海<br />\n有信念能同仇敵慨<br />\n曲線勇敢說出來<br />\n講小器 我威絕世代<br />\n<br />\n傻仔至乜都痴呆<br />\n城市已潰毀不來<br />\n佛法西天佑蔭風氣開<br />\n誓殺滅盲從全為愛<br />\n即使戰鬥鍵盤外<br />\n我夢遺與天地同在<br />\n我夢遺與方丈同在<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n澳門獨立運動<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/macauindependen/status/1084111292376395776\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmacauindependen%2Fstatus%2F1084111292376395776&d=lH%2FTjTKhyl%2BMcbfhgwPB7xv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=98e7e29c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmacauindependen%2Fstatus%2F1084111292376395776&h=f602e1a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/macauindependen/status/1084111292376395776</a><br />\n<br />\n澳門獨立 Macau independent<br />\n2019年1月12日<br />\n<br />\n自1999年以來，在特區政府統治之下，澳門民生問題每日增加，澳門公民被中國政府系統性滅絕，澳門特區政府並非澳門人的政府，澳門人被拒絕在民主體制之外。因此，我們宣佈，推動澳門獨立運動，成立真正澳門人的國家。<br />\n<br />\n我們主張澳門主權未定論。《西里亞發條約》國際體系發明之前，葡國已進入澳門。《中葡友好通商條約》並未提及澳門主權問題。1971年聯合國出賣香港澳門，被剔除殖民地名單外。1974年葡萄牙政府單方面宣佈澳門是「葡萄牙管中領土」並未於法理上及自決原則上詢問過澳門人。因此，澳門在法理上是無主地。<br />\n<br />\n澳門獨立，脫華歸歐。<br />\n澳門作為遠東最早之歐洲港口，有五百年之歐洲傳統累積，比任何一東亞國家早進入西洋文明。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2016/04/11/131111/澳門獨立的法理基礎/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.vjmedia.com.hk%2Farticles%2F2016%2F04%2F11%2F131111%2F%E6%BE%B3%E9%96%80%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E7%9A%84%E6%B3%95%E7%90%86%E5%9F%BA%E7%A4%8E%2F&d=lH%2FTjTKhyl%2BMcbfhgwPB7xv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=1e3b4fea\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2016/04/11/131111/澳門獨立的法理基礎/</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：Donago<br />\n<br />\n澳門主權未定論<br />\n<br />\n在《友好條約》當中，並未提出有關澳門主權的問題，加上《和好條約》已經被代替（有說法是中葡有默契地未廢除和條約，但默契不代表具有法律效力），以及在中國及葡萄牙國內都發生了政權轉移的情況以下，指向的事實便是由於舊的條約已經失效，加上新的條約並未包含有關主權問題的條文之下，可以總結的，是澳門以往由中葡共享的主權已經不再生效&mdash;澳門的主權的「未定的」。葡萄牙人在澳門擁有的，僅是實然上的殖民管治權，而主權問題在澳門，仍是未曾處理的問題。<br />\n<br />\n因此，在澳門主權未定以下，澳門人有權在一九四五年聯合國成立後，根據四五年的《聯合國憲章》當中的第一條及第五十五條、一九六零年的《聯合國大會第一五一四號決議》的第二條，以及一九六六年《公民及政治權力國際公約》的第一條，以住民自決的方式來決定澳門的政治前途。"},{"pid":"ebb7589f72e5ab672112345167bc8e9a8ff6b528","tid":986210,"uid":109462,"like":7,"dislike":36,"score":-29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T09:17:12.000Z","msg":"老實講，以澳門嘅體量，併入香港國咪算囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e14f59063f37f2e854347630a8df44365353124b","tid":986210,"uid":33028,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T09:21:56.000Z","msg":"就算「自決」都唔覺得會有多數人支持獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e37a41e3fd77268b61f94a1faf4a8389fcb8319f","tid":986210,"uid":143241,"like":5,"dislike":27,"score":-22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T09:27:50.000Z","msg":"澳門頂盡都淨係可以做到香港嘅藩屬,根本唔可以獨立咁生存<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71333bd0ef1d833da3039715db182351324527c9","tid":986210,"uid":35430,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T10:11:44.000Z","msg":"淪陷左9成終於識醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連登著名澳門仔點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6331587ac2cdb603f58e45ad2a2cbfdb6f725ce4","tid":986210,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T10:22:13.000Z","msg":"澳門立國，隨時珠海都併入澳門"},{"pid":"24f072f5d1065a88aceccd591bfeac352ebd5986","tid":986210,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T16:16:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2281e75dbc1e6a308ef3b9729faab2a2a2ff524c","tid":986210,"uid":987,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T16:20:09.000Z","msg":"澳門難以生存，無賭即收皮，靠中國黎賭姐係要睇人頭"},{"pid":"a70e0fcc8f76d67e6092617483d3e87348aa2715","tid":986210,"uid":51129,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T16:22:00.000Z","msg":"澳門唯一優勢就係全國唯一賭場<br />\n冇支那人養住個賭場，成個澳門等食屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f671c93c4c5b075a272d5f3a32ad1666507aec4","tid":986210,"uid":525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T16:24:13.000Z","msg":"@玄學大師xxx"},{"pid":"3adf3702e8140ac34f49aa1d3f71e84531d919f3","tid":986210,"uid":163350,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T16:25:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4cc49f735aae7043b1b323c125e5a5d221e24d3f","tid":986210,"uid":50328,"like":8,"dislike":8,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T20:04:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aa3d955008f1f90feb842ae582f7f5e589c79de0","tid":986210,"uid":226955,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T20:18:40.000Z","msg":"100年後支國假想：<br />\n<br />\n廣東廣西統一 -&gt; 兩廣共和國<br />\n內外蒙統一 -&gt; 大蒙古國<br />\n東北三省 -&gt; 滿洲國<br />\n新疆 -&gt; 東突厥斯坦<br />\n台灣 -&gt; 台灣共和國<br />\n西藏 -&gt; 吐蕃<br />\n上海 -&gt; 滬國<br />\n香港 -&gt; 香港國<br />\n澳門 -&gt; 澳門國"},{"pid":"f200bf7c7a5c2c83bf0cc0d01687e552e3bc58bc","tid":986210,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T20:28:10.000Z","msg":"劉明官擦"},{"pid":"f1c86da8ba1bbd1f4832b612ff3b234edaddeb27","tid":986210,"uid":186549,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T20:44:55.000Z","msg":"打住澳門獨立旗號好快比人拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個黃司長惡過香港班奶共官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"752087702bdbe51fb8eab6ae015fea49a468636c","tid":986210,"uid":5489,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T20:59:05.000Z","msg":"澳門有23條都敢咁揚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"093ae5310d508b9798fdbfad15691af176e4db37","tid":986210,"uid":81113,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"aa3d955008f1f90feb84